message: @leah didnt see session 6....anything awesome? (other than Lifeproof, Ive seen their demo..which is sweet).

Of the 11 companies in the two sessions the judges all picked Room77 as their fav. except for Kevin Rose who picked Savings.com Wrap-up with the judges starts here: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5CD-OiY1iKY&feature=player_detailpage#t=3371s

Savings.com Boom! (they were a 2.0 competitor) ShopSquad.com has a lot of potential.  Others were Lifeproof Cases 140Fire & Minglebird. Judges were Greg Tseng, Aaron Patzer, Kevin Rose, Cyan Banister, Mo Koyfman Kara Swisher.
